body_html: @gunan, thanks for your information. I use a little-endian version of PowerPC. Optimally I would like TF to work out of the box and it has more or less been the case in the past, it would be a pity that we can no longer do it because of a less-than-often-used part. Can you tell me what's the best way to reach the BoringSSL team?
